<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>呼吸系统疾病 on Aloha's Blog</title><link>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/</link><description>Recent content in 呼吸系统疾病 on Aloha's Blog</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Sun, 30 Oct 2022 15:19:11 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>慢性支气管炎</title><link>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E6%85%A2%E6%80%A7%E6%94%AF%E6%B0%94%E7%AE%A1%E7%82%8E/</link><pubDate>Thu, 03 Nov 2022 22:16:19 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E6%85%A2%E6%80%A7%E6%94%AF%E6%B0%94%E7%AE%A1%E7%82%8E/</guid><description>&lt;dl>
&lt;dt>慢性支气管炎（chronic bronchitis）| 慢支&lt;/dt>
&lt;dd>指气管、支气管黏膜及其周围组织的慢性非特异性炎症。&lt;/dd>
&lt;/dl>
&lt;p>临床上以&lt;strong>咳嗽&lt;/strong>、&lt;strong>咳痰&lt;/strong>为主要症状，或有&lt;strong>喘息&lt;/strong>，&lt;ins>每年持续发病 3 个月及以上，连续 2 年及以上&lt;/ins>，并排除具有咳嗽、咳痰、喘息症状的其他疾病。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>慢性阻塞性肺疾病</title><link>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E6%85%A2%E6%80%A7%E9%98%BB%E5%A1%9E%E6%80%A7%E8%82%BA%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/</link><pubDate>Thu, 03 Nov 2022 09:13:03 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E6%85%A2%E6%80%A7%E9%98%BB%E5%A1%9E%E6%80%A7%E8%82%BA%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/</guid><description>&lt;dl>
&lt;dt>慢性阻塞性肺疾病（chronic obstructive pulmonary disease，COPD）| 慢阻肺&lt;/dt>
&lt;dd>特征是&lt;strong>持续存在的&lt;/strong>呼吸系统症状和&lt;strong>气流受限&lt;/strong>（实质），通常与显著暴露于有害颗粒或气体引起的气道和（或）肺泡异常有关。&lt;/dd>
&lt;/dl>
&lt;p>肺功能检查，在吸入支气管扩张剂后，&lt;strong>FEV&lt;sub>1&lt;/sub>/FVC &amp;lt; 70%&lt;/strong>（诊断标准）表明存在持续气流受限。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>支气管哮喘</title><link>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E6%94%AF%E6%B0%94%E7%AE%A1%E5%93%AE%E5%96%98/</link><pubDate>Fri, 04 Nov 2022 22:37:43 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E6%94%AF%E6%B0%94%E7%AE%A1%E5%93%AE%E5%96%98/</guid><description>&lt;dl>
&lt;dt>支气管哮喘（bronchial asthma）| 哮喘&lt;/dt>
&lt;dd>是一种以&lt;em>慢性气道炎症&lt;/em>和&lt;em>气道高反应性&lt;/em>为（基本）特征的异质性疾病。&lt;/dd>
&lt;/dl>
&lt;p>临床表现为反复发作的喘息、气急、胸闷或咳嗽等症状，常在夜间或凌晨发作或加重（迷走神经兴奋，气道管径↓），多数病人和自行缓解或经治疗后可缓解（可逆性气流受限）。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>支气管扩张症</title><link>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E6%94%AF%E6%B0%94%E7%AE%A1%E6%89%A9%E5%BC%A0%E7%97%87/</link><pubDate>Fri, 04 Nov 2022 23:17:31 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E6%94%AF%E6%B0%94%E7%AE%A1%E6%89%A9%E5%BC%A0%E7%97%87/</guid><description>&lt;dl>
&lt;dt>支气管扩张症（bronchiectasis）| 支气管扩张&lt;/dt>
&lt;dd>主要指急、慢性呼吸道&lt;em>感染&lt;/em>和支气管&lt;em>阻塞&lt;/em>后，反复发生支气管化脓性炎症，致使&lt;strong>支气管壁结构破坏&lt;/strong>，管壁增厚，引起支气管异常和持久性扩张的一类异质性疾病的总称。&lt;/dd>
&lt;dd>可以是原发/继发，主要分为囊性纤维化（cystic fibrosis, CF）/非囊性纤维化导致的支气管扩张，这里主要讨论前者。&lt;/dd>
&lt;dd>临床表现主要为&lt;span class="inline-list">&lt;span class="inline-list-item">慢性咳嗽（通过病程长短与&lt;a href="https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E8%82%BA%E9%83%A8%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E6%80%A7%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E8%82%BA%E8%84%93%E8%82%BF/">肺脓肿&lt;/a>鉴别）、&lt;/span>&lt;span class="inline-list-item">咳大量脓痰&lt;/span>&lt;span class="inline-list-conjunction">和（或）&lt;/span>&lt;span class="inline-list-item">反复咯血&lt;/span>&lt;/span>。&lt;/dd>
&lt;/dl></description></item><item><title>肺结核</title><link>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E8%82%BA%E7%BB%93%E6%A0%B8/</link><pubDate>Fri, 04 Nov 2022 23:09:18 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E8%82%BA%E7%BB%93%E6%A0%B8/</guid><description/></item><item><title>肺癌</title><link>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E8%82%BA%E7%99%8C/</link><pubDate>Fri, 04 Nov 2022 23:11:58 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E8%82%BA%E7%99%8C/</guid><description/></item><item><title>间质性肺疾病</title><link>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E9%97%B4%E8%B4%A8%E6%80%A7%E8%82%BA%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/</link><pubDate>Sat, 19 Nov 2022 13:45:19 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E9%97%B4%E8%B4%A8%E6%80%A7%E8%82%BA%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/</guid><description/></item><item><title>肺血栓栓塞症</title><link>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E8%82%BA%E8%A1%80%E6%A0%93%E6%A0%93%E5%A1%9E%E7%97%87/</link><pubDate>Sat, 19 Nov 2022 12:00:07 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E8%82%BA%E8%A1%80%E6%A0%93%E6%A0%93%E5%A1%9E%E7%97%87/</guid><description/></item><item><title>肺动脉高压与肺源性心脏病</title><link>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E8%82%BA%E5%8A%A8%E8%84%89%E9%AB%98%E5%8E%8B%E4%B8%8E%E8%82%BA%E6%BA%90%E6%80%A7%E5%BF%83%E8%84%8F%E7%97%85/</link><pubDate>Sat, 